Intrathecal baclofen is also indicated for the management of severe spasticity of the cerebral or spinal original in patients 4 years of age and older. It is reserved for patients unresponsive to oral baclofen therapy, or those who experience intolerable central nervous system side effects at effective doses. For use in spasticity due to traumatic brain injury, baclofen should be considered after at least one year of injury.[L39429]', '6221094501622', '', 3305, '2024-09-04', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(17896, 'Drakon body whitening cream 50 gm', 'داركون كريم تبيض للجسم 50 جم', '', '175', 'Liquorice+kojic acid+vitamin c+titanium dioxide+aloe vera+panthenol', 'Xfactor medical > pharma cruise medical', 'Cream', 'كريم', 'تفتيح وتوحيد لون الشرة', 'Skin care', '50 gm', 'drakon body whitening cream acts as an emollient and humectant to regenerate and soften skin especially rough area (elbow heel knee) by drawing moisture to the surface and sealing it in. drakon body whitening cream contains concentrated active complex tha', '6223008330649', '', 847, '2022-05-30', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(30024, 'Zonivan 100 mg 20 caps', 'زونيفان 100مجم 20 كبسول', '56', '76', 'Zonisamide', 'Horus for pharmaceutical products', 'Cap', 'كبسولة', '', 'Anti-epileptic.sulfonamides', '100 mg', 'Zonisamide capsules are indicated as adjunctive therapy in the treatment of partial seizures in adults with epilepsy.[L42530] Zonisamide oral suspension is indicated as adjunctive therapy for the treatment of partial-onset seizures in adults and pediatric patients 16 years of age and older.[L42535]', '', '', 908, '2025-08-15', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(26470, 'Salfoverose 20mg/5ml syrup 120ml', 'سالفوفيروز 20مجم/5مل شراب 120 مل', '', '12', 'Zinc sulphate', 'Averroes pharma-egypt', 'Syrup', 'شراب', '', 'Zinc supplement', '20mg', 'Zinc can be used for the treatment and prevention of zinc deficiency/its consequences, including stunted growth and acute diarrhea in children, and slowed wound healing. It is also utilized for boosting the immune system, treating the common cold and recurrent ear infections, as well as preventing lower respiratory tract infections [L2172].', '6224008179160', '', 1603, '2022-06-18', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(20184, 'Haes-steril 10% i.v.infusion (n/a)', 'هيس-ستريل 10% محلول', '', '54', 'Hydroxyethyl starch', 'Fresenius kabi', 'Unknown', 'غير محدد', '', 'Plasma expander', '10%', 'An intravenous solution of hydroxyethyl starch is used to prevent shock following severe blood loss caused by trauma, surgery, or other issues.', '', '', 778, '2022-07-30', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(27136, 'Sodium bicarbonate 8.4% (sunny pharma.) i.v. inf. vial 50 ml', 'صوديوم بيكربونات صني فارما 8.4 % فيال حقن وريدي 50 مل', '', '20', 'Sodium bicarbonate', 'Sunny medical', 'Vial', 'فيال', 'يعادل حموضة الجسم -- يزيد من قلوية الدم -- يقلل من اعراض الحموضة و الترجيع', 'Alkalinizer', '8.4%', 'Sodium bicarbonate is used for the treatment of metabolic acidosis which may occur in severe renal disease, uncontrolled diabetes, circulatory insufficiency due to shock or severe dehydration, extracorporeal circulation of blood, cardiac arrest and severe primary lactic acidosis. Also is indicated in severe diarrhea which is often accompanied by a significant loss of bicarbonate. Further indicated in the treatment of certain drug intoxications, including barbiturates (where dissociation of the barbiturateprotein complex is desired), in poisoning by salicylates or methyl alcohol and in hemolytic reactions requiring alkalinization of the urine to diminish nephrotoxicity of blood pigments.', '', '', 1399, '', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(28341, 'Topotel 1mg/ml 4mg vial', 'توبوتيل 1مجم/مل 4مجم فيال', '', '1,000', 'Topotecan', 'Fresenius kabi > egyptian group for import and export', 'Vial', 'فيال', '', 'Antineoplastic', '1mg', 'For the treatment of advanced ovarian cancer in patients with disease that has recurred or progressed following therapy with platinum-based regimens. Also used as a second-line therapy for treatment-sensitive small cell lung cancer, as well as in combination with cisplatin for the treatment of stage IV-B, recurrent, or persistent cervical cancer not amenable to curative treatment with surgery and/or radiation therapy.', '', '', 648, '2022-08-04', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(9899, 'Risperdal 2mg 20 f.c. tab.', 'ريسبيردال 2مجم 20 اقراص', '143', '190', 'Risperidone', 'Janssen cilag > soficopharm', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Psychiatric.antipsychotics', '2mg', 'Risperidone is indicated for the treatment of schizophrenia [L12885,L44692,L46297] and irritability associated with autistic disorder.[L12885] It is also indicated as monotherapy, or adjunctly with lithium or valproic acid, for the treatment of acute mania or mixed episodes associated with bipolar I disorder.[L12885,L44692]
Risperidone is additionally indicated in Canada for the short-term symptomatic management of aggression or psychotic symptoms in patients with severe dementia of the Alzheimer type unresponsive to nonpharmacological approaches.[L12906]
Risperidone is also used off-label for a number of conditions including as an adjunct to antidepressants in treatment-resistant depression.[A177226]', '', '', 2388, '2024-11-28', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(21160, 'Jenax 10 sachets', 'جيناكس 10 اكياس', '', '115', 'Gelatin (collagen) hydrolysate+vitamin c', 'Pharma zad > resipi pharma', 'Sachet', 'أكياس', '', 'Antirheumatic.osteoarthritis.anabolic agents', '', 'Gelatin is used for weight loss and for treating osteoarthritis, rheumatoid arthritis, and brittle bones (osteoporosis). Some people also use it for strengthening bones, joints, and fingernails. Gelatin is also used for improving hair condition and to shorten the recovery after exercise and sports-related injury [L2113]. Gelatin is used in preparations of foods, cosmetics, and medicine [L2113].
Plasma volume expander in hypovolaemic shock [L2115]. Haemostatic [L2115].
Gelatin-based hydrogels are being used in drug delivery and tissue engineering because they are able to promote cell adhesion and proliferation. In addition, these hydrogels can be used as wound dressings because of their attractive fluid absorbance properties. Manufacturing technologies such as ultraviolet stereolithography and two-photon polymerization can be used to prepare structures containing photosensitive gelatin-based hydrogels [L2111].', '', '', 1007, '2022-07-12', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(32061, 'Oria diaper rash cream 75 gm', 'اوريا دايبير راش كريم 75 جم', '', '89', 'Zinc oxide+calendula extract+chamomile extract+vitamin c+castor oil++olive oil+honey+aloe vera+glycerin+panthenol', 'Hi care pharmaceutical and cosmotics > unimax', 'Cream', 'كريم', '', 'Diaper rash cream', '75 gm', 'Zinc can be used for the treatment and prevention of zinc deficiency/its consequences, including stunted growth and acute diarrhea in children, and slowed wound healing. It is also utilized for boosting the immune system, treating the common cold and recurrent ear infections, as well as preventing lower respiratory tract infections [L2172].', '', '', 1163, '2023-03-09', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(3758, 'Swalena 125 ml anti-dandruff lotion', 'سوالينا لوشن مضاد لقشرة الشعر 125 مل', '', '199', 'Capixyl+saw palmetto extract+rosemary extract+horsetail extract+capsicum extract+lactic acid+salicylic acid+kernel oil+propylene glycol+panthenol+sesame oil', 'Swa pharma for pharmaceuticals', 'Lotion', 'لوشن', '', 'Hair tonic lotion spray', '125 ml', '', '', '', 913, '2025-05-16', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(22061, 'Advanced vitamin c 30 gummies', 'ادفانسد فيتامين سي 30 قطعة', '', '599', 'Vitamin c', 'Vitalife', 'Unknown', 'غير محدد', '', 'Vitamin c', '', 'For the treatment of vitamin A deficiency.', '', '', 784, '2022-08-03', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(28806, 'Decanerve 30 caps.', 'ديكانيرف 30 كبسولة', '165', '210', 'Vitamin b1+vitamin b2+vitamin b3+vitamin b5+vitamin b6+vitamin b7+vitamin b9+vitamin b12+choline+inositol', 'WELLNESS PHARMA', 'Cap', 'كبسولة', '', 'Multivitamins', '', 'For the treatment of vitamin A deficiency.', '6224010479388', '', 2356, '2025-07-30', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
